</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"SprintGrooming(BacklogRefinement)-Conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
<p>Sprint Grooming is an essential activity in Scrum that helps teams stay =
aligned, plan effectively, and improve delivery efficiency. By refining bac=
klog items before Sprint Planning, teams can ensure a smooth development cy=
cle, reduce uncertainty, and focus on delivering high-quality software effi=
ciently.</p>
